OL,3,CYoung drivers buying fake policies
OL,4,Closing #2,000 on average, says insurer
OL,6,FThis includes the average premium paid
OL,7,Fto a ghost broker (#1,700) and the
OL,8,Fextra fees (#300) charged by ghost
OL,9,Fbrokers selling fraudulent policies.
OL,11,FAviva said ghost broking detections
OL,12,Fare running higher this year than in
OL,13,F2024.
OL,15,FGhost brokers are not real insurance
OL,16,Fbrokers but criminals luring motorists
OL,17,Fin with fake policies that appear
OL,18,Fcheap.
