OL,3,CYoung drivers buying fake policies
OL,4,Closing #2,000 on average, says insurer
OL,6,FThey may produce insurance documents
OL,7,Fthat are entirely fake and bypass
OL,8,Flegitimate insurers completely, or
OL,9,Ffalsify someone's details to
OL,10,Fartificially bring down the cost, or
OL,11,Ftake out a genuine policy but then
OL,12,Fcancel it.
OL,14,FOften people do not realise their
OL,15,Finsurance is fake until they are
OL,16,Fstopped by police or involved in an
OL,17,Faccident.
