OL,4,Closing #2,000 on average, says insurer
OL,6,FMany scams start on social media and
OL,7,FAviva said it has identified a sharp
OL,8,Frise in ghost broking scams using
OL,9,Ffake, professional-looking websites
OL,10,Fthat impersonate legitimate insurers.
OL,12,FOwen Morris, UK personal lines chief
OL,13,Fexecutive at Aviva, said, "Ghost
OL,14,Fbroking is a fast-growing criminal
OL,15,Fenterprise that targets young drivers
OL,16,Fon social media sites.
