OL,4,Closing #2,000 on average, says insurer
OL,6,F` Verify who you are dealing with.
OL,7,FContact insurers directly and check
OL,8,Fthe Financial Services Register. Check
OL,9,Fregistrations with the British
OL,10,FInsurance Brokers' Association (Biba)
OL,11,Fand the Financial Conduct Authority.
OL,12,FBiba can help young drivers, who often
OL,13,Fpay more for their policies, to find
OL,14,Flegitimate insurance.
OL,16,F` Anyone suspecting they have been a
OL,17,Fvictim of ghost broking or other fraud
OL,18,Fshould report their concerns to the
OL,19,Fpolice.
